reviewText: Bought as a gift. He listened to it right away, enjoyed it, and plans to listen to it again.
Great Present for the guy who likes to fish catfish

The copy I received is Defective. Half the chapters do NOT play. I tried it in three (3) different
DVD systems and get the same results! How do I go about reimbursement from Boguss seller?

You know, I purchased this as a gift for my son-in-law.  That man loves to fish.  I thought he would like this video.  I haven't seen it of course as it is a gift..It was shipped on time and in good condition and I know my son-in-law will like it too.
